The Englishmen are still waiting to be formally introduced to each other

So, you didn\'t hear about the infinitesimally weird result the OPERA team were getting? It\'e been in the news a lot recently.

OK, so the result is almost certainly a mistake, but any mistake is fuel for humour however tenuous the connection!

The latest episode of the Skeptic\'s Guide to the Universe podcast even mentions the most likely cause for that mistake. I forgot what exactly it is, but it produces an effect that matches the anomaly perfectly. So yeah, turns out the laws of physics aren\'t overturned after all.
